description._content: Description: Sanaa, and the mosque of Salah El-Din Location: Sanaa, Yemen Date: 1952 Description: General view of Sanaa and Salah El-Din's mosque. Location: Sanaa, Yemen Date: 1952 Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/677 This image is part of the Colonial Office photographic collection held at The National Archives. Feel free to share it within the spirit of the Commons Please use the comments section below the pictures to share any information you have about the people, places or events shown.
